    "\n",
    "### **Success Criteria Assessment**\n",
    "\n",
    "| Criterion | Target | Achieved | Status |\n",
    "|-----------|--------|----------|--------|\n",
    "| Binary F1 Score | ≥ 0.80 | 0.8086 (Naive Bayes) | ✅ Met |\n",
    "| Multiclass Weighted F1 | ≥ 0.70 | 0.6726 (SVM) | ⚠️ Narrowly missed |\n",
    "\n",
    "The binary classification target has been met. The multiclass target was narrowly missed by 0.03 points — SVM achieved 0.6726 against a target of 0.70. This gap is attributable primarily to the extremely poor performance on the Negative class, which pulls the weighted F1 down despite strong Neutral class performance. Addressing class imbalance is the clearest path to closing this gap in future iterations."
